name: Degrenade Buster
description: Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must first be Special Summoned (from your hand) by banishing 2 Cyberse monsters from your GY. (Quick Effect): You can target 1 monster your opponent controls whose ATK is higher than this card's; banish it until the End Phase. You can only use this effect of "Degrenade Buster" once per turn.
